differentes fonctions:

mlx_init: Initialises the MLX library. Must be called before using any other functions.

mlx_new_window: Creates a new window instance.

mlx_hook: Registers events.

mlx_loop: Loops over the MLX pointer, triggering each hook in order of registration. // maintenir les differents events successif

mlx_xpm_file_to_image: Converts an XPM file to an MLX image pointer. // a voir apres avoir choisi les images

mlx_put_image_to_window: Puts your image to the screen at the given coordinates. //voir comment poser les differentes images

mlx_destroy_image: Frees the image. // fonction de free

mlx_destroy_window: Frees the window instance.

mlx_destroy_display: Frees MLX.

The map can be composed of only these 5 characters:
0 for an empty space,
1 for a wall,
C for a collectible,
E for a map exit,
P for the playerâ€™s starting position.

